{"tid":1469663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[得罪講句] 成日話前線乜乜柒柒果d","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:03:06.000Z","uid":163076,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7211b53c4b928ded1a023c5fee5988282743e1e7","tid":1469663,"uid":163076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:37:39.000Z","msg":"利申左先： 前線做乜都好，比前線決定，不割蓆不分化<br />\n<br />\n琴日咁多人屌鳩前線，老實講，果堆點算係前線先<br />\n當有臥底既時候，仲要見到唔係一個半個<br />\n講緊係一堆一堆，仲分別演緊唔同角色，我地既思考方向就已經唔係咁單一同班狗對立<br />\n<br />\n好多人都話個公安係班狗送黎比人捉，搞混亂，然後防暴清場，嚇走和理非<br />\n咁點解唔可以諗多步，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連果班捉公安既人，都係臥底黎</span></span></strong>，目的係包圍目標人仕再挑起各位情緒，制造混亂，要既人都唔洗好多，10令個最埋到去既人已經做到呢個效果<br />\n<br />\nQA:<br />\nQ1: 呢個可能性大唔大？<br />\n我覺得60%，因為成個運動開始左2個幾月，從來，係從來，都無手足會屌立場，屌first aid<br />\n<br />\nQ2： 如果係咁點破？<br />\n都係果句，不割蓆不分化，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>永遠支持手足決定</ins></strong></span><br />\n同時灌輸比其他人知黑警做緊上面講緊既事，明白之後更加唔會分化，佢地再玩多幾次就入到個官印象，呢樣都幫到手足打甩暴動罪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>再重申，核彈都唔割</ins></strong></span><br />\n拋磚引玉，有錯請屌"},{"pid":"0c851a02cbf2b15b09b813af627d252817bc49c1","tid":1469663,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:38:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a858e083a7376217aef699029c00ae472d1cbd30","tid":1469663,"uid":163076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c851a02cbf2b15b09b813af627d252817bc49c1","tid":1469663,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:38:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"我都覺得唔應該focus係捉鬼，搶得太多foc<br />\n要捉鬼既果班由佢捉<br />\n但唔好比佢帶到風向者"},{"pid":"3439ea9